data.description: **Highly Motivated Seller has reduced the price** Meticulously updated single-family residence in North Hollywood's Prime Residential area. Step into the warm, inviting ambiance of this newly remodeled, bright, and airy home. The open living and dining spaces surround an all-new custom eat-in kitchen with a spacious "L" shaped butcher block countertop/breakfast bar, new stainless steel appliances, a farmhouse sink, and a built-in microwave cabinet. Glass doors open the dining area to a charming patio for breezy moments at sunset or while attending to laundry. The two-car finished garage is transformed into an inviting 360 SF outdoor "Bonus" living space making the total living area 1624 SF on a generous 6,791 sqft corner lot. The secured yard features a lush lawn, a prolific lemon tree, and a Ficus tree hedge. Recent upgrades include electrical, plumbing, HVAC, kitchen, appliances, flooring, windows, tile, finishes, insulation, drywall, paint, recessed lighting, landscaping, Brand new Ring alarm system, video doorbell, wifi-controlled driveway gate, pedestrian gates, Brand new mini split, and fan in the garage. Possible RV access. Ideally located near NoHo Arts District, NoHo West, Jamie Beth Slavin Park, with convenient access to Burbank Airport and 170 FWY.
